column5: Shutting the site down gave me lots of good fishing time today. Met up with my buddy, the Smerch, and we had a blast. Took a little while to figger out what the little buggers wanted, but once we did.  WooHoo!   We kept 2 dozen as dinner guests out of the hundred odd caught.  I played camera man today. Didn't want to bust the lens on my mug  Going to go to sleep soon. No OFC for 2 nights had me bouncing off the walls.
